Package me.chloe.raiderlib

Class RaiderLib

java.lang.Object
edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.SubsystemBase
me.chloe.raiderlib.RaiderLib
All Implemented Interfaces:
edu.wpi.first.util.sendable.Sendable, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.Subsystem
public class RaiderLib extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.SubsystemBase
Subsystem that handles MovingParts as well as the ability to easily switch between Differential, Mecanum, and Swerve drive systems without needing to change anything more than a few Constants. This Robot Code template is very useful in helping guarantee the sucess of the idea that Team 1518 will continue to progress on the software side of things as this project makes using advanced control (aka PIDControl) very simple.
